48:34.230 --> 48:37.599
<i>I fell from the olive tree,</i>

48:37.600 --> 48:41.030
<i>who will help me get up?</i>

48:41.140 --> 48:44.269
<i>A girl with dark hair</i>

48:44.270 --> 48:47.950
<i>offering her hand.</i>

48:48.350 --> 48:51.280
I have never seen
so many people at a wedding.

48:51.770 --> 48:54.729
You father laid many seeds,
now you reap the benefits.

48:54.730 --> 48:57.729
<i>A girl with dark hair,</i>

48:57.730 --> 49:02.200
<i>that is what I want for me!</i>

49:04.060 --> 49:05.360
Thank you!

49:07.560 --> 49:10.240
<i>Tarara wears</i>

49:10.770 --> 49:13.320
<i>a green dress</i>

49:13.980 --> 49:16.360
<i>full of ruffles</i>

49:16.520 --> 49:19.280
<i>and of jingle bells.</i>

49:19.890 --> 49:24.179
<i>Tarara yes,</i>

49:24.180 --> 49:27.310
<i>Tarara no,</i>

49:28.060 --> 49:34.490
<i>Tarara, a girl that has
caught my eye</i>

49:35.060 --> 49:38.269
<i>Tarara wears</i>

49:38.270 --> 49:40.889
<i>a pair of trousers</i>

49:40.890 --> 49:46.190
<i>that from top to bottom
are all buttons.</i>

49:46.930 --> 49:50.850
<i>Tarara yes,</i>

49:51.980 --> 49:55.450
<i>Tarara no,</i>

49:56.100 --> 50:02.610
<i>Tarara, a girl that has
caught my eye</i>

50:08.680 --> 50:10.889
<i>Aii, you crazy Tarara</i>

50:10.890 --> 50:13.389
<i>Move your waist</i>

50:13.390 --> 50:15.809
<i>for the boys</i>

50:15.810 --> 50:18.269
<i>of the olive trees</i>

50:18.270 --> 50:22.929
<i>Tarara yes, Tarara no,</i>

50:22.930 --> 50:24.850
What's the matter woman?

50:25.270 --> 50:28.740
They are happy.
Today everyone is happy.

50:29.850 --> 50:30.889
No.

50:30.890 --> 50:32.730
I am alone in my house.

50:33.430 --> 50:36.730
At least they will give us sons.
And maybe a daughter!

50:37.100 --> 50:39.280
It's only a matter of time.

50:40.140 --> 50:43.270
My daughter has good hips,
and your son is strong.

50:43.310 --> 50:48.530
<i>Tarara, a girl that has
caught my eye.</i>

50:51.850 --> 50:53.450
Be happy!

50:54.180 --> 50:58.100
For those that are here,
and those that aren't.

51:00.100 --> 51:02.990
- Long live the newlyweds!
- Long live!

51:04.310 --> 51:05.900
Be happy...

51:19.520 --> 51:20.700
I love you.

51:22.730 --> 51:24.030
I love you.

51:26.560 --> 51:28.490
Hold me and don't let go.

51:32.230 --> 51:33.650
I won't.

53:02.600 --> 53:05.740
I had that thorn in my side,
now it has gone.

53:06.020 --> 53:09.139
At last our lands will be united.

53:09.140 --> 53:11.840
- What are your talking about father?
- Leonardo.

53:12.060 --> 53:14.960
- What about Leonardo?
- You will have a good legacy!

53:15.520 --> 53:19.950
That small orchard that was wedged
between my fields, at last I sold it.

53:21.140 --> 53:24.179
He says that he wants to get out of here,
that there is nothing left here for him.

53:24.180 --> 53:27.330
He is leaving, with his wife
and his son to the mountains.

53:35.600 --> 53:36.990
What's the matter?

53:38.310 --> 53:40.450
- It's nothing father.
- Look at you!

53:40.850 --> 53:43.650
If your mother could see
you she would be so happy.

53:43.810 --> 53:45.110
Do you think so?

53:50.890 --> 53:52.190
Where are you going?

53:52.230 --> 53:55.280
- Should I go with you?
- No, stay here with the others.

55:56.560 --> 55:59.610
<i>That moon...</i>

56:02.390 --> 56:05.480
<i>That moon...</i>

56:08.930 --> 56:13.640
<i>The moon leaves a knife</i>

56:15.310 --> 56:19.740
<i>abandoned in the air,</i>

56:22.270 --> 56:26.360
<i>that, being a lead threat,</i>

56:26.810 --> 56:31.860
<i>lusts after bloody pain.</i>

57:00.180 --> 57:01.890
Let me come in.

57:02.430 --> 57:06.140
I come frozen through
walls and windows!

57:07.180 --> 57:11.890
Open the roofs and breasts
where I can warm up!

57:17.390 --> 57:20.270
I am cold, I am cold...

57:20.980 --> 57:22.530
I am cold.

57:25.230 --> 57:28.530
My ashes of somnolent metals

57:28.810 --> 57:31.360
search for the fire's crest...

57:32.140 --> 57:34.980
in the woods and in the streets.

57:35.930 --> 57:40.480
Well this night there will be
red blood in my cheeks...

57:41.930 --> 57:46.600
and on the reeds that will be clustered
at the wide feet of the wind.

57:47.680 --> 57:51.810
There is no shadow, nor ambush...

57:52.140 --> 57:54.890
that can't escape.

57:56.270 --> 57:58.950
I want to enter into a breast...

57:59.560 --> 58:02.269
that will give me warmth.

58:02.270 --> 58:04.490
A heart for me...

58:05.270 --> 58:06.860
a warm heart.

58:08.520 --> 58:12.240
I want to wander
the mounts of my breast.

58:13.980 --> 58:15.860
Let me in...

58:20.810 --> 58:22.280
Let me...

58:25.140 --> 58:26.440
Daughter!

58:31.560 --> 58:33.280
What are you doing here?

58:35.520 --> 58:37.400
What are you doing here?

58:40.890 --> 58:42.980
What is wrong, my child?

58:43.520 --> 58:46.200
I am afraid, I am afraid father...

58:46.640 --> 58:51.480
We all are, but don't tell your husband.
We should all be happy.

58:53.390 --> 58:55.890
Do you know how much
this wedding cost?

58:58.100 --> 58:59.530
Yes... I do.

58:59.890 --> 59:03.019
Well... let's go inside.
Let's enjoy it while we can.

59:03.020 --> 59:06.400
They are already leaving
for the lower plains...

59:06.640 --> 59:08.480
You first father...

59:15.430 --> 59:17.190
- Don't be long...
- I won't.

